# Local host-environment bookkeeping (e.g. HumOS's own nested-checkout
# index note) — never part of this repo's own public content; must never be
# tracked/pushed. Untracked-but-not-ignored here previously tripped the
# docs-lint ghost-project check as a false alarm for the outer monorepo's
# own bucket path.
/INDEX.md

