build/
# EXCEPTION: `docs/operational/build/` is a documentation directory (the
# build-system docs hub: build-system.md, ci-cd-integration.md, …), not a
# Python build artifact. Without these negations the broad `build/` rule
# above excludes it from version control, so CI's clean checkout has ~14
# broken links into it (docs-lint fails). Same failure class as the
# `**/output/` vs `infrastructure/validation/output/` collision.
!docs/operational/build/
!docs/operational/build/**
develop-eggs/
dist/
downloads/
eggs/
